                <h2>Current Weather in Honolulu (Waikiki)</h2>
                <p align="center">
                  <a class="weatherwidget-io" href="https://forecast7.com/en/21d31n157d86/honolulu/?unit=us" data-label_1="HONOLULU" data-label_2="WEATHER" data-theme="pure" >HONOLULU WEATHER</a>
